@ifnottex
@node Top
@top Heirloom Darwin Port

This document is the Info-format index for the Heirloom Darwin port,
a downstream port of Gunnar Ritter's Heirloom Project to macOS 26.4
arm64.

@strong{Not authoritative.}  Upstream is
@url{http://heirloom.sourceforge.net/} (unmaintained since about 2008).
This port is for compatibility, not scholarship or production
reliance.

For per-tool documentation, run @command{man @var{tool}} against the
Heirloom man tree at @file{/opt/heirloom/share/man/5man/}.

@end ifnottex

