@node Legacy
@chapter Legacy Compatibility Posture

The port preserves compatibility with prior-system artefacts:

@itemize
@item @command{cpio} — old-ASCII / new-ASCII / binary / character
      cpio format variants all readable and writable.
@item @command{tar} — v7 and USTAR tar formats.
@item @command{sccs} — all SCCS history file formats.
@item @command{pkgadd} — SVR4 package format v1 and v2.
@end itemize

Where a legacy format could not be preserved on Darwin, the reason
is documented per-tool.

