@chapter Provenance

Chain of custody:

@display
Bell Labs / AT&T  →  Sun (OpenSolaris)  →  Ritter (Heirloom Project)
    →  moonman81 (Darwin port, 2026)
@end display

Per-repo @file{PROVENANCE.md} has the full detail.

